data.description: Discover this stunning home featuring the popular Boardwalk floor plan that has been meticulously upgraded. A sizable paver driveway & lush tropical landscaping welcome you. Step inside to find a bright & spacious open layout with recessed lighting & new ceiling fans throughout. The heart of the home has been transformed into a culinary haven with the addition of a kitchen island, ample soft-close cabinetry, backsplash, sparkling quartz countertops, stainless steel range & microwave, under-mount work station sink, & new fixtures all complemented by a large pantry & breakfast bar. Both bathrooms feature new vanities, quartz countertops & upgraded fixtures. The backyard is a private oasis enclosed by a vinyl privacy fence with a 10' double-gated entry. This smart home is equipped with a security system with window & door sensors, video doorbell, & smart panel for peace of mind. Additional upgrades include a water softener system, TV wall mounts throughout, & exterior equipment privacy enclosure. No HOA fees, no CDD fees & no flood insurance required! Ideally located in close proximity to Pine Island Rd & an abundance of shopping & dining.
